import React from 'react'

import {
    Container,
    ContainerProfile,
    Title,
    Photo,
    Name,
    ContainerBody,
    ContainerCheckBox,
    ContainerAlignRow,
    Align,
    TextSex,
} from './styles'

import { Controlled } from '../../components/Form/Controlled'

import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form'
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';

export function Profile() {

    const { control } = useForm()

    return (
        <Container>
            <ContainerProfile>
                <Title>Meus dados</Title>
                <Photo></Photo>
                <Name>Mateus Nascimento</Name>
            </ContainerProfile>

            <ContainerBody>
                <Controlled
                    name='name'
                    control={control}
                    placeholder='Nome completo' placeholderTextColor="#3C3C3C"
                />
                <Controlled
                    name='cpf'
                    control={control}
                    placeholder='CPF' placeholderTextColor="#3C3C3C"
                    type="cpf"
                />
                <Controlled
                    name='dateNasc'
                    control={control}
                    placeholder='Data de nascimento' placeholderTextColor="#3C3C3C"
                    type="date"
                />

                <ContainerCheckBox>
                    <ContainerAlignRow>
                        <Align>
                            <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                            <TextSex>Feminino</TextSex>
                        </Align>
                        <Align>
                            <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                            <TextSex>Masculino</TextSex>
                        </Align>
                    </ContainerAlignRow>
                    <Align style={{ marginTop: 10 }}>
                        <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle-outline" size={24} color="#D3E0E2" />
                        <TextSex>Prefiro n√£o responder</TextSex>
                    </Align>
                </ContainerCheckBox>
            </ContainerBody>
        </Container>
    )
}
